finalData.name: THE EDIT
finalData.description: The Edit at d3 is a luxury residential development by Meraas located in the heart of the Dubai Design District (d3). The project features modern architecture with a focus on designer living, offering high-end apartments with spacious layouts, balconies, and premium finishes. The development includes Tower A and offers a lifestyle integrated with Dubai's creative hub.
